OL,6,FHe said: "It could be we are seeing
OL,7,Fthe emergence of a new normal in which
OL,8,Fcase 2025 will resemble 2024, or the
OL,9,Fregulators could make a further push
OL,10,Fto get back to pre-pandemic levels."
OL,12,FWhile traditional A*-G grades are used
OL,13,Ffor GCSE in Northern Ireland and
OL,14,FWales, these have been replaced in
OL,15,FEngland with a 9-1 system, where 9 is
OL,16,Fthe highest.
OL,18,FA 4 is broadly equivalent to a C
OL,19,Fgrade, and a 7 is broadly equivalent
OL,20,Fto an A.
